VALUES
  ('elementary-d0d1b9a2-moex-00835', 'elementary-d0d1b9a2', 'elementary-d0d1b9a2-moex-110-01c5eaab', 'sub-elementary-d0d1b9a2-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列「」內的動物，何者在成語中含有「人品性格」的象徵意義？', '["塞翁失「馬」", "驚弓之「鳥」", "「鶴」立雞群", "「狐」群狗黨 引「狼」入室"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:30:49+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "983a9bc5fc3b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "35b7bb1ab497", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "509", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "國文(包括公文格式用語)", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 44, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "會計"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-d0d1b9a2-moex-00836', 'elementary-d0d1b9a2', 'elementary-d0d1b9a2-moex-110-01c5eaab', 'sub-elementary-d0d1b9a2-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '「繁華擾攘的羅東鎮，藏著一條名為『浮崙巷』的小徑，巷名充滿文藝感。名稱取自於當地舊名『浮崙仔』， 由於該區地勢高，水患淹不到，遠看像是浮出水面的車輪而得名。隨著街區發展更迭，周邊發展出夜市和商 圈，浮崙巷『鬧中取靜』，只有在地人知道的捷徑，獨樹一格成為文藝風小巷。在地文史工作者說，浮崙巷 正是在地鄉土作家黃春明出生地，早期著作《鑼》便是起源於此。」 這則報導從那幾個面向介紹「浮崙巷」？', '["地名由來", "特產小吃", "街巷特色", "著名地標 在地名人"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:30:49+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "983a9bc5fc3b", "answer_pdf_sha1": "35b7bb1ab497", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "509", "s": "0101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "國文(包括公文格式用語)", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 45, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "會計"}'::jsonb, NULL),
